@chapter Libraries
@cindex Libraries

This chapter describes the features of the libraries of which Crystal Space
consists. There are certain dependencies between libraries which enforce a
sort of hierarchy.  If you are developer actually working on Crystal Space,
you should be careful not to introduce circular dependencies into the library
graph.  @xref{Dependencies}.

